  description: Increases Magic Resistance by 5 and starting mana by 15. Every 3 seconds,
    the wearer and all adjacent allies restore 3% of their Maximum Health and 10
    Mana. A shimmering, gold-trimmed mantle that pulses with a warm, golden light;
    it is a manifestation of pure celestial grace, providing both physical healing
    and spiritual clarity to those who stand within its light.
